Package.Author: Pogs / DaMatz
Package.Description:
Pogs Contour Icons - continued by DaMatz (2019-) thx DaMatz 
Pogs Contour Icons - continued by Solo (2017-2018) thx Solo

abbreviations:
DMG - damage | PEN - penetration | RLD - reload
HP - Hit Points | VR - view range | FSR - front sides rear

De​sc​ri​ption:
PENETRATION - It’s average penetration with standard AP shell, in gold gold shells
DAMAGE - It’s avarage damage with standard AP shell, HE shell for artillery
ARMOR - It’s normal - nothing in pack name - or FSR:
- Normal - REAR·SIDES·FRONT armor RSF
- FSR - FRONT·SIDES·REAR armor
HP - Hit points with upgraded turret
View range - view range with upgraded turret
Reload time - time to reload gun / drum in autoloader

Package.Name: Real Time v{version} [by {author}]
Package.Author: HAWG
Package.Description:
Instead of the red and green tanks at the top of your screen during battle you now have colored icons matching those in the players panel. When a tank is destroyed there icon is deleted from the list. With a quick glance you can see how many heavies, meds, lights etc.... are left on each team. 

Added is cross informer when a team mate dies an white cross will flash on the minimap for a few seconds at the location where it was killed at.

If a enemy dies an orange cross will flash on the minimap for a few seconds at the location where it was killed at.

If a platoon mate dies an blue cross will flash on the minimap for a few seconds at the location where it was killed at.
